{"tid":859614,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[總之入黎啦]美女眾多不能盡錄 2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈投選專區","createTime":"2018-10-12T15:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T14:39:52.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c18b84b6bff9c250f1d632633713ccb66a085e24","tid":859614,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(非)文凱玲vs陳潔玲(甲)<br />\n(乙)蘇麗珊vs吳嘉熙@SG(甲)<br />\n(非)伍樂怡vs李蔓瑩(非)<br />\n(甲)賴慰玲vs湯洛雯(甲)<br />\n(非)鄧月平vs曾淑雅(非)<br />\n(非)趙希洛vs卓楓而(非)<br />\n(乙)鄺潔楹vs張沛樂(甲)<br />\n(乙)鄭宇澄vs麥美恩(甲)<br />\n(非)雨僑vs周秀娜(非)<br />\n(乙)林映蔚vs陳自瑤(甲)<br />\n(非)呂慧儀vs簡幗儀(甲)<br />\n(乙)駱文捷vs衛詩雅(乙)<br />\n(乙)陳華鑫vs譚嘉儀(模)(甲)<br />\n(甲)姚子羚vs梁凱寧(甲)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3c6064f71eb54d43ba14ebb6cf7cf320679a7a9","tid":859614,"uid":92376,"like":18,"dislike":65,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-10-13 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/i99Y8bh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi99Y8bh.png&h=cc12e04e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tbmba6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ftbmba6E.png&h=cfe343ff&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(非聯)文凱玲vs陳潔玲(甲13)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"88429f910dd462030eacfcc7f95f819481636bbf","tid":859614,"uid":92376,"like":24,"dislike":53,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-10-13 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xygyQhp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxygyQhp.png&h=ce762580&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CzaJ2ap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCzaJ2ap.png&h=5f94b7c2&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(乙18)蘇麗珊vs吳嘉熙@SG(甲16)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"e626e3699ebf8674c8a6af5faa51f072f97e6058","tid":859614,"uid":92376,"like":44,"dislike":44,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-10-13 12:04am-10:04pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aX5xni0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaX5xni0.png&h=deaa6094&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kVdAtCn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht